'''erotophobia'''

#[[Fear]] of or [[disbelief]] in [[romantic]] [[relationship]] or its aspects or related things.
#(''controversially'') Political or religious organizations or viewpoints that are concerned with limiting or restraining some aspect(s) of sexuality.

